+ New changes
1. Implemented TAP mechanism, now we need to use TAP to prepare the food and to serve the customer instead of drag.
2. Use DOUBLE TAP to throw some food items or burnt items to dustbin.
3. Insta Cook : Helps to cook food items instantly
4. Burn Proofer : Avoid over burning of food items
5. Coins Doubler : It double's earned coins at the end of level
